{"lemma":"تُحْفَةٍ","slug":"تُحْفَةٍ","root":"ت.ح.ف","root_slug":"ت-ح-ف","root_link":"/words/roots/ت-ح-ف","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n3791"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AA%D9%8F%D8%AD%D9%92%D9%81%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"masterpiece, curiosity, rarity"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/tuħ.fa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n3791","headword_ar":"تُحْفَةٌ","root":"tHf","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tuHafapN","text_ar":"تُحَفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K, &c.)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bir~N","text_ar":"بِرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A gratuitous gift,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"favour;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a bounty,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"benefit"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laTafN","text_ar":"لَطَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a present;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing sent to another in token of courtesy"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"honour"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (K;) in some copies of the K,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"luTof","text_ar":"لُطْف"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) [i. e.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AltHfp","text_ar":"التحفة"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A^atoHafota bihi Alr~ajula","text_ar":"مَا اَتْحَفْتَ بِهِ الرَّجُلَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mina Albir~i waAll~aTafi","text_ar":"مِنَ البِرِّ وَاللَّطَفِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;) or [simply]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A^atoHafota bihi","text_ar":"مَا اَتْحَفْتَ بِهِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gayoraka","text_ar":"غَيْرَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Turofap","text_ar":"طُرْفَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which properly signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a gift not given to any one before;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of which the recipient did not possess the like, and which pleases him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of fruit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of sweet-smelling flowers:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) [it generally means simply"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a present;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a rare,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pleasing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rare and pleasing, present:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tuHafN","text_ar":"تُحَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, K.) Accord. to some, it is originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wuHofapN","text_ar":"وُحْفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K, TA:) Az says that its"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t","text_ar":"ت"},{"kind":"text","text":"is originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tawaH~afa","text_ar":"تَوَحَّفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is quasi-pass. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^atoHafahu","text_ar":"اَتْحَفَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Lth, TA:) so that it should be mentioned in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wHf","text_ar":"وحف"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K, TA:) being like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tuhamapN","text_ar":"تُهَمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tuxamapN","text_ar":"تُخَمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. (TA.) It is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tuHofapu AlS~aAy^imi Ald~uhonu wa Almijomaru","text_ar":"تُحْفَةُ الصَّايِمِ الدُّهْنُ وَ المِجْمَرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The pleasing present for the faster is oil, and aloes-wood"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; i. e., these dispel from him the grievousness and distress occasioned by the fasting. (TA.) And in another, respecting dates,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tuHofapu","text_ar":"تُحْفَةُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alkabiyri waSumotapu AlS~agiyri","text_ar":"الكَبِيرِ وَصُمْتَةُ الصَّغِيرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. The date is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the pleasing gift for the big,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"full-grown,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"old, and the quieter of the little one,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"child"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And in another,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tuHofapu Almuw^omini Almawotu","text_ar":"تُحْفَةُ المُوْمِنِ المَوْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The boon for the believer is death"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","TA","K","Lth"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}